  "description": "PGP Desktop 10.0.x before 10.0.3 SP2 and 10.1.0 before 10.1.0 SP1 does not properly implement the \"Decrypt/Verify File via Right-Click\" functionality for multi-packet OpenPGP messages that represent multi-message input, which allows remote attackers to spoof signed data by concatenating an additional message to the end of a legitimately signed message, related to a \"piggy-back\" or \"unsigned data injection\" issue.",
